#User Stories

#1 As a new user I want to create a new checking account
#2 As a user, I want to be able to login 
#3 As a user I want to deposit a fund
#4 As a user I want to withdraw funds
#5 As a user I want to check my balance
#6 As a user I want to transfer fund from one account to the other

#DDBB

User Table:
-userId (PK)
-username
-password

Account Table:
-accountId (PK)
-balance
-userId (FKey)

Transaction Table:
-transactionId (PK)
-transactionType
-userId (FK references user(Id))
-amount
-timeStamp
-accountId (FK references account(Id))


